title: Traffic stopped on M1 between Leeds and Wakefield after 'multi-vehicle collision'
text:
Highways England @HighwaysYORKS Follow #M1 #WestYorkshire S/B J40-J39 We're getting reports of a multi vehicle collision partially blocking the carriageway @ highwaysneast en route
16:37 - 15 Sep 2015 Retweet Reply Favourite Highways England @HighwaysYORKS Follow Delays are starting to build on approach to the scene of the collision on #M1 S/B J40-J39. Recovery is en route.
16:59 - 15 Sep 2015 Retweet Reply Favourite Highways England @HighwaysYORKS Follow #M1 S/B J40-J39 traffic has been temporarily stopped to allow recovery and carriageway clean-up work to take place. Please bear with us.
17:39 - 15 Sep 2015 Retweet Reply Favourite Last updated Tue 15 Sep 2015 Travel West Yorkshire
